This is the second release of ka_noviceshroud 
i took the comments and made a second version, 
called ka_manfly_noviceshroud_v2 

ive cluttered it up a little bit, 
making the outer areas of the map more chalenging to play in,
creating a locker room. A good place to rumble,
or even the propane stash, or perhaps the storage corner. 
either way its going to be good. 
the lighting is fast and the fps 
are great, even in the fray.


Cons: 

because of the way the light 

effects were created it makes 

bot travel in the map impossible... 

sry no nav. file
